{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 322663, "create_time": 1659339917, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "同好奇 相当于是不约而同都选择了平面直角坐标系诶", "timestamp": 1659339917}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 322725, "create_time": 1659343115, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "猜测一下可能的原因。一是我们生活在一个平面上，（虽然地球是圆的，但对人来说都是平地），那平时生活指方向就是在二维上指，前后左右之类的。第二人体是对称的，类似一个六面体，四个侧面是腹面背面两侧手脚，行动方式是向着腹面方向直线前进，这很容易导致人们把方向分为类似直角坐标系的坐标轴。如果人是个三棱柱，也许以120度分的三个方向会更方便。第三，人喜欢找参照物，不止辨认方向和位置是如此，会通过比较新到的地方和原来的地方是否相似来判断是否是同一个地方，而且能认下固定不变的东西，并以此为参照来展开活动，这也方便了人类活动，毕竟忘了家在哪岂不是要再建一个会很麻烦。于是在发现不变的东西，比如北极星，结合前面所说，就会创造类似四个方向的指示词。第四，因地而异，四方向指示词的使用情况可能不同，比如在狭长河谷地带，城市依河而建，人们生活中以河为据的方向指示会被常用，比如“沿河往上游走”“去河对岸往山脚下走”。", "timestamp": 1659343115}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323009, "create_time": 1659358158, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cardinal_direction\n除了Bob所说的，还有指南针，不同季节的风向，还有古代天文学研究", "timestamp": 1659358158}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323021, "create_time": 1659358598, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Carol: 首先得有“南”，然后才能有 指南针。你该不会认为人们有了指南针后才有东南西北吧？", "timestamp": 1659358598}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323026, "create_time": 1659358896, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Dave: 有了“南”还得统一啊？你该不会认为“南”指的就是同一个东西吧", "timestamp": 1659358896}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323052, "create_time": 1659359820, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Carol: 我的天，你真以为人类最初发明的”南“是用指南针定义的啊？", "timestamp": 1659359820}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323056, "create_time": 1659359932, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Dave: Re Dave: 我的天，你不会觉得指南针没有促进人类对东南西北的认识吧", "timestamp": 1659359932}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323059, "create_time": 1659360014, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Dave: 我觉得这是很简单的道理啊，起源可以有多个", "timestamp": 1659360014}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323164, "create_time": 1659365115, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "看看东和西的甲骨文，我猜东象形太阳升起，西象形太阳落下", "timestamp": 1659365115}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323170, "create_time": 1659365293, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "然后描述二维方向需要两个向量，所以添加南北，南象形正午太阳方向", "timestamp": 1659365293}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323175, "create_time": 1659365405, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "山南水北为阳，山北水南为阴，南北应该来自阳光投影", "timestamp": 1659365405}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 323210, "create_time": 1659366433, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Eve: 好家伙咱俩想一块去了", "timestamp": 1659366433}], "create_time": 1659339745, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1659366433, "likenum": 8, "n_attentions": 8, "n_comments": 12, "pid": 91717, "poll": null, "reply": 12, "text": "为什么汉语有东西南北，英语也有对应的词，为什么两波人不约而同定义了这四个方向呢", "timestamp": 1659339745}}